      <p id="Par41">The proportions of the mixture components were drawn from binomial distributions using the values of <italic>λ</italic>, <italic>θ</italic>, and <italic>θʹ</italic>, with <italic>θ'</italic> representing the <italic>θ</italic> parameter for outliers, where<disp-formula id="Equj"><alternatives><tex-math id="M29">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
